<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Your Exclusive Graduate Offer | Transform Strong</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700;800;900&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
 
  :root {
    --teal: #5BBCB8;
    --teal-dark: #2E8B87;
    --teal-deep: #1A5C59;
    --charcoal: #1C1C1C;
    --warm-white: #FAF9F7;
    --mid-gray: #6B6B6B;
    --light-border: #E0DCDC;
  }
 
  body {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    background-color: var(--warm-white);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
 
  /* HEADER */
  .site-header {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    padding: 18px 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .logo-lockup {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .logo-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
  }
  .logo-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--teal);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .logo-text span {
    display: block;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
 
  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal-deep) 0%, var(--teal-dark) 50%, var(--teal) 100%);
    padding: 72px 24px 64px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px; right: -60px;
    width: 280px; height: 280px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -80px; left: -40px;
    width: 200px; height: 200px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 54px);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: #B8EAE8;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2.5vw, 20px);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
  }
 
  /* HOMEWORK CONFIRM */
  .homework-bar {
    background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--teal);
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .homework-bar h2 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal-deep);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .homework-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .hw-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--warm-white);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--light-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .hw-check {
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    background: var(--teal);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .hw-check svg { width: 11px; height: 11px; }
 
  /* FORM SECTION */
  .form-section {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 24px 64px;
  }
  .form-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .form-intro h2 {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 30px);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .form-intro p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-style: italic;
  }
 
  /* GHL FORM PLACEHOLDER */
  .ghl-form-wrapper {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--light-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 36px 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .ghl-embed-note {
    background: #F0FAF9;
    border: 1.5px dashed var(--teal);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--teal-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
 
  /* Fallback visible form fields for preview */
  .form-field {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .form-field label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 7px;
  }
  .form-field input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 13px 16px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--light-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    background: var(--warm-white);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    outline: none;
  }
  .form-field input:focus {
    border-color: var(--teal);
  }
  .form-submit {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 16px;
    background: var(--teal-deep);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 8px;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
  }
  .form-submit:hover { background: var(--teal-dark); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .form-submit:active { transform: translateY(0); }
  .form-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    margin-top: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
 
  /* WHAT HAPPENS NEXT */
  .next-steps {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 48px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .next-steps h3 {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .steps-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .step-card {
    flex: 1 1 180px;
    max-width: 200px;
  }
  .step-num {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--teal);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .step-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
 
  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }
 
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .ghl-form-wrapper { padding: 24px 18px; }
    .steps-row { gap: 16px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
 
<header class="site-header">
  <div class="logo-lockup">
    <svg class="logo-icon" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <rect x="4" y="8" width="32" height="4" rx="2" fill="#5BBCB8"/>
      <rect x="4" y="16" width="22" height="4" rx="2" fill="#5BBCB8"/>
      <rect x="4" y="24" width="28" height="4" rx="2" fill="#5BBCB8"/>
      <rect x="4" y="32" width="16" height="4" rx="2" fill="#5BBCB8"/>
    </svg>
    <div class="logo-text">
      Transform
      <span>Strong</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
 
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">🎉 Masterclass Complete</div>
  <h1>You showed up.<br><em>Now claim your reward.</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">You've done what most people never do — you finished the work. Here's what's waiting for you on the other side.</p>
</section>
 
<div class="homework-bar">
  <h2>Homework Complete ✓</h2>
  <div class="homework-steps">
    <div class="hw-step">
      <div class="hw-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none"><path d="M2 6l3 3 5-5" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
      Introduced yourself in Skool
    </div>
    <div class="hw-step">
      <div class="hw-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none"><path d="M2 6l3 3 5-5" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
      Posted your #1 goal commitment
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
 
<section class="form-section">
  <div class="form-intro">
    <h2>Enter your info to unlock your exclusive coaching discount</h2>
    <p>Just for masterclass graduates — I'll send your personalized offer link straight to your inbox.</p>
  </div>
 
  <div class="ghl-form-wrapper">
 
    <!-- ============================================================
         GHL EMBED GOES HERE
         In GoHighLevel:
         1. Create a new Form (Forms > Builder)
         2. Fields: First Name, Last Name, Email, Phone
         3. On submit: add to "Masterclass Graduate" contact tag
